  <div class="stackedit__html"><h2 id="cosmic-symphony-exploring-the-interplay-of-shiva-shakti-and-the-universe"><strong>Cosmic Symphony: Exploring the Interplay of Shiva, Shakti, and the Universe</strong></h2>
<p><img src="https://files.oaiusercontent.com/file-pPy8nXfy9qDClnw0jfJR0p5Y?se=2023-12-15T19%3A08%3A11Z&amp;sp=r&amp;sv=2021-08-06&amp;sr=b&amp;rscc=max-age%3D31536000%2C%20immutable&amp;rscd=attachment%3B%20filename%3Dacb9afc9-7aa8-495a-bb51-dff88ba910f4.webp&amp;sig=Cu2v0TTBCFR0drW6fB1o7p72qiqScqW0i9FcIbpi50I%3D" alt="Generated by DALL·E"></p>
<h2 id="sanskrit-verse">Sanskrit Verse:</h2>
<p>शिवः शक्त्या युक्तो यदि भवति शक्तः प्रभवितुं<br>
न चेदेवं देवो न खलु कुशलः स्पन्दितुमपि।<br>
अतस्त्वाम् आराध्यां हरिहरविरिञ्चादिभिरपि<br>
प्रणन्तुं स्तोतुं वा कथमकृतपुण्यः प्रभवति॥१॥</p>
<h2 id="breaking-sandhi">Breaking Sandhi:</h2>
<p>शिवः शक्त्या युक्तः यदि भवति शक्तः प्रभवितुम्<br>
न चेत् एवं देवः न खलु कुशलः स्पन्दितुम् अपि।<br>
अतः त्वाम् आराध्यां हरि-हर-विरिञ्च-आदिभिः अपि<br>
प्रणन्तुम् स्तोतुम् वा कथम् अकृत-पुण्यः प्रभवति॥</p>
<h2 id="verse-source">Verse Source:</h2>
<p>Saundarya Lahari, Verse 1</p>
<h2 id="english-translation">English Translation:</h2>
<p>When united with Shakti, Shiva is endowed with the ability to create.<br>
Otherwise, the God cannot even pulsate.<br>
Therefore, how can one who has not performed meritorious deeds,<br>
Worship or praise You, who is worshipped even by Hari, Hara, Virinchi, and others?</p>
<h2 id="transliteration">Transliteration:</h2>
<p>śivaḥ śaktyā yukto yadi bhavati śaktaḥ prabhavitum<br>
na cedevam devo na khalu kuśalaḥ spanditumapi.<br>
atastvām ārādhyāṁ hariharaviriñcādibhirapi<br>
praṇantum stotuṁ vā kathamakṛtapuṇyaḥ prabhavati.</p>
